title: Suspend fees of privacy accounts to boost adoption
body:
Should we suspend the fees of the privacy accounts for a limited time (eg. 4-8 weeks) to boost adoption?

The privacy accounts are not used a lot, it may help to suspend the fees for a few weeks to boost the adoption. We can also use this campaign to spread the word about the privacy accounts another time.
choices: YES, suspend the fees of privacy accounts to boost adoption
author: 0x63Dbf00C99EaD0635FF5aDf2fd2f1F7F2141fc7C
